channel.title: My customs one of a kind key blade
channel.description: well ive browsed mopars models quite a few times and ive cam across some very wounder-full key blade models and i wanted to make one so i decided to start on my very own customs keblade bases of off sol(sun) and luna(moon) ik the color scheme isnt the best but i was hoping that some one would give me advise leading to a better color scheme ..this is my first key blade and i do say so myself i think the wire frame is good looking and ive posted a side view of the wireframe so i dont get accused of it being flat

zyle1992:

Ok, seriously. Kingdom Hearts pisses me off. One, think about this. How the hell do you “hold” the “keyblade”? I mean look at the fucking hilt for shit’s sake. And, how the hell can a key be a blade? By definition, a key is not in any way sharp. So how the fuck can it be a blade?

  1. Hold it by the handle, dumbass
    2.It’s a blade because it’s sharp, and if you played the game, you would understand the key part.
